# Baby Journal Server

Environment variables - copy this to .env and fill in your values.

## Database
DATABASE_URL="postgresql://user:password@localhost:5432/baby_journal"

## JWT
JWT_SECRET="your-jwt-secret-change-this-in-production"

## File Storage
UPLOAD_DIR="./uploads"
# Max file size in bytes (default 100MB)
MAX_FILE_SIZE="104857600"

## Server
PORT="3000"
NODE_ENV="development"

## SMS Login (optional, for phone verification)
# SMS_PROVIDER="aliyun"
# SMS_ACCESS_KEY=""
# SMS_ACCESS_SECRET=""
# SMS_SIGN_NAME=""
# SMS_TEMPLATE_CODE=""
